{"document_id": "uuid-3e19f65670c0", "chunk_id": "0021", "text": "IO Software Stack (24)\nHigh-level IO libraries\n Provide structured data abstraction for scientific applications.\n Better describe how the application accesses shared storage resources.\nParallel IO applications (link)\n Access high-level IO, MPI-IO, and Posix IO libraries.\n Access MPI-IO and POSIX IO libraries.\n Access POSIX IO library directly.", "source": "txt", "token_count": 345, "metadata": {"original_filename": "(자문)hpc_system_software_20241127.txt", "text_hash": "3e19f65670c0", "text_length": 4655, "split_info": {"chunk_size": null, "stride": null, "min_length": 50, "total_chunks": 24}, "created_at": "", "tags": [], "origin": "사내 문서"}}
